  "title": "Infant Care Teacher @ Tampines Junction (MRT) Learning Kidz",
  "description": "<p><strong>Positions :</strong></p>\n<p>Infant Care Teacher ( Chinese Language / English Language Teacher)</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits :</strong></p>\n<p>· Established Childcare centre <strong>located at TAMPINES (5 mins to MRT)</strong></p>\n<p>· Good career prospects and developments</p>\n<p>· Attractive remuneration packages, bonus and benefits</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· <strong>Salary range from $1,800 to $3100) Depending on qualification and experience and posting)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Must possess at least one of the following Early Childhood certification:-</p>\n<p>1. Advanced Certificate in Early Years (<strong>ACEY</strong>)</p>\n<p>2. Certificate In Infant &amp; Toddler Care (<strong>CIT</strong>)</p>\n<p>3. Higher Certificate in Infant Care (<strong>HCIC</strong>)</p>\n<p>4. DPL Certificate (L1 or L2)</p>\n<p>· Registered with ECDA as <strong>EY1 or EY2 Or L2 or L1</strong></p>\n<p>· Good communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>· Fresh graduates are welcome</p>\n<p>· Able to commence work soon is preferred.</p>\n<p>· To work as a team</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please state your expected salary.</p>\n<p><strong>ATTRACTIVE MONTHLY INCENTIVE PAYOUT and other Incentives and benefits</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Call Cecilia at 90690910 or resume to email:cecilia@learningkidz.com.sg.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Please copy and paste to activate this link.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>https://v2.taidii.com/hr/job_posting/detail/?job_id=NDc=&amp;center_id=MTA0Nw==</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
